This is the backend and client-side of a simulation inspired by the **Primer** YouTube channel. It explores how autonomous agents ("blobs") behave, interact, and evolve over time in a virtual world called **Blobbington**.

As a hobbyist, self-taught, and AI-supported developer, my goal is to build a flexible simulation framework that models emergent behavior and societal change.

